          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLhSX1FSiv7z2KrYL1zAanvfq2AT_HcY7L23WboWWiuSWyM7g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "I have nothing but positive things to report in regards to my appointment at Madison Dental. I scheduled online and the staff reached out to me the same day to confirm and even offer to move me up to an earlier date. The staff at checkin were incredibly welcoming and kind. The wait was very brief and I was shown back to a room within 15 minutes (most of that 15 minutes was just me filling out my paperwork). I was seen by Dr. Okon who was incredibly friendly, understanding, and helpful. He answered all of my questions, took time to work through the issues I was dealing with, and helped me set up a clear and actionable plan to move forward with. at no point in my visit did I feel rushed nor did I feel my issues were dismissed. I regretfully forget Dr. Okon\u2019s assistant\u2019s name, but she too was incredibly lovely. From start to finish I had a fantastic experience with Dr. Okon and the staff at Madison dental and I will be returning!",
